			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">KEI? SoW? Lots of INT gear? Don't need it.
<br />
Stromm player, level 40, 161 INT, VS. Oasis packed with 9 Sand Giants running amok.
<br />

<br />
Pulled up focus Air, gave him daggers and plate, BOII and went to town. Pulled with Malaise, and shot pet a DS. Had both heals memmed to cycle heals...when SG reached 80% - Blaze- cycled heals till SG at 40 - Blaze - cycled another heal if needed - Blaze- ...SG turning tail - Shock - SG dead. Pet at 50-70%, usually 10m left. Rinsed and repeated. Me 8, SG's 0...(left one standing to keep everyone on their toes) 170+ plat in FS and coin, and happy peeps xping in Oasis. Took me a little over an hour, no deaths, no gates, so down time wasn't bad. I'm positive HG's are easier, and if it looks like yer not gonna win, safety's just a gate away.
<br />

<br />
You don't know what you can do 'til ya try.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
